    <tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
    <description>Produces electricity from sunlight. Does not work in the dark. A really small version of the normal solarpanel, generates a lot less electricity, but at least you can harness the sun through a smaller hole in the roof</description>
    <size>(1,1)</size>
    <costList>
      <Steel>20</Steel>
